"With WRP-1396 (Q1 2018) we are trying to do the Subscriber lookup before the COB/MOSA processing.  We want to do this because the SubDOB can be relevant in the COB processing, but there are cases where the SubDOB is captured poorly, not corrected, then not contributing to the COB processing correctly.  However, because the lookup can be driven by the MOSA contractID I am putting one version in output_837 that only runs (again) if the MOSA contractID is populated.  The one in output_SplitSOR will run on the Pat or Master Contract ID.  - jdm 01/2018"
